<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="the-instant-that">the instant (that)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>一…就：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The instant (= As soon as) she stopped asking questions, I got up and went out of the room.
她一停止问问题，我就起身走出了房间。</p><footer>北师大⑤ – 14</footer></div></div>